DISCLAIMER:

This is a MOCK payment system for testing and development purposes only.
All transactions use fake money and are not real financial transactions.

This software is NOT intended for:
- Real payment processing
- Production financial systems
- Handling actual money
- Processing real credit card information
- Any regulated financial activities

For real payment processing, please use established payment providers such as:
- Razorpay (https://razorpay.com)
- Stripe (https://stripe.com)
- PayPal (https://paypal.com)
- Square (https://squareup.com)
